---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title="Loja e Carrinho - Documentacao" adm={true} activePage="/admin/docs">
  <div class="docs-layout">
    <aside class="docs-sidebar">
      <nav class="docs-nav">
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Getting Started</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs">Visao Geral</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/structure">Estrutura</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Sistema</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/auth">Autenticacao</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/store" class="active">Loja e Carrinho</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/ai">Inteligencia Artificial</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Backend</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/database">Banco de Dados</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/api">APIs</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-nav-section">
          <h3>Configuracao</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/env">Variaveis de Ambiente</a></li>
            <li><a href="/admin/docs/commands">Comandos</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </aside>

    <main class="docs-content">
      <h1><Icon name="lucide:shopping-cart" size={24} /> Sistema de Loja e Carrinho</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        O carrinho de compras e totalmente <strong>client-side</strong>, utilizando localStorage para
        persistencia e o padrao Observer para atualizacoes em tempo tempo real na interface.
      </p>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:database" size={20} /> Arquitetura</h2>
      <p>
        O sistema utiliza Astro DB (Turso) para dados de produtos e localStorage para o carrinho.
        Essa separacao permite que o carrinho funcione mesmo em ambientes onde o banco de dados
        nao esta disponivel.
      </p>

      <h3>Componentes Principais</h3>
      <div class="files-list">
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/lib/cart/store.ts</code>
          <span>Classe CartStore com padrao Observer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/lib/cart/client.ts</code>
          <span>Gerenciador de UI para interacoes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/pages/api/cart/</code>
          <span>Endpoints de sincronizacao (placeholder)</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:zap" size={20} /> Padrao Observer</h2>
      <p>O CartStore implementa o padrao Observer para notificar subscribers sobre mudancas:</p>

      <pre>// Inscreve para receber atualizacoes
cartStore.subscribe((state) => {'{'}
  updateCounter(state.items.length);
  renderCartModal(state);
{'}'});

// Adiciona item
cartStore.addItem({'{'}
  productId: string;
  name: string;
  price: number;
  quantity: number;
  image: string;
{'}'});

// Remove item
cartStore.removeItem(productId);

// Atualiza quantidade
cartStore.updateQuantity(productId, quantity);</pre>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:package" size={20} /> Estrutura do Produto</h2>
      <p>Os produtos sao armazenados no Astro DB com a seguinte estrutura:</p>

      <pre>Products {'{'}
  id: string;           // UUID unico
  name: string;         // Nome do produto
  description: string; // Descricao detalhada
  price: number;        // Preco em centavos
  image: string;        // URL da imagem
  category: string;     // Categoria do produto
  featured: boolean;    // Produto em destaque
  visible: boolean;     // Visivel na loja
  createdAt: Date;     // Data de criacao
{'}'}</pre>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:palette" size={20} /> Componentes de Interface</h2>
      <div class="files-list">
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/components/ProductCard/</code>
          <span>Card de produto com botao adicionar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/components/CartModal/</code>
          <span>Modal do carrinho com controles</span>
        </div>
        <div class="file-item">
          <Icon name="lucide:file-code" size={16} />
          <code>src/components/CartButton/</code>
          <span>Botao flutuante com contador</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:moon" size={20} /> Modo Escuro</h2>
      <p>Os controles de quantidade (+/-) possuem estilos dedicados para modo escuro:</p>

      <pre>.qty-btn {'{'}
  background: #333;
  color: #f4f2f4;
  border-color: #444;
{'}'}

[data-theme='dark'] .qty-btn:hover {'{'}
  background: #444;
{'}'}</pre>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:layout-grid" size={20} /> Seo de Produtos</h2>
      <p>A pagina de loja exibe produtos em um grid responsivo:</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Desktop:</strong> 4 colunas</li>
        <li><strong>Tablet:</strong> 2 colunas</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile:</strong> 1 coluna</li>
      </ul>

      <h2><Icon name="lucide:settings" size={20} /> Configuracao</h2>
      <p>Para exibir produtos no carrinho, os componentes ProductCard precisam dos atributos:</p>
      <pre>data-product-id={'{'}product.id{'}'}
data-name={'{'}product.name{'}'}
data-price={'{'}product.price{'}'}
data-image={'{'}product.image{'}'}</pre>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-layout {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 70px auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .docs-sidebar {
    width: 260px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 90px;
    height: fit-content;
    max-height: calc(100vh - 110px);
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .docs-nav {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section h3 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
  }

  .docs-nav-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .docs-nav-section a {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .docs-nav-section a:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-10);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .docs-nav-section a.active {
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-20);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .docs-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .docs-content h1 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content h1 svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .docs-content h2 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-primary-alpha-20);
  }

  .docs-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .docs-content h2 svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .docs-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .docs-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .docs-content p {
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content code {
    font-family: monospace;
    background: var(--color-primary-alpha-10);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .docs-content pre {
    background: var(--color-gray-900);
    color: #f8f8f2;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .docs-content ul {
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .docs-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '->';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .files-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .file-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.875rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .file-item svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .file-item code {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .file-item span {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .docs-layout {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .docs-sidebar {
      width: 100%;
      position: static;
    }

    .docs-nav {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-nav,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h1,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h2,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content h3 {
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content p,
  :global([data-theme='dark']) .docs-content li {
    color: #a0a0a0;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .file-item {
    background: #252525;
    border-color: #333;
  }

  :global([data-theme='dark']) .file-item code {
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }
</style>
